---
description: Resolve latest tool versions with mise before writing config
alwaysApply: true
---

Before writing or changing any tool/runtime version in this repo, do not guess from memory.

Required process:
1. Run `scripts/resolve-tool-version.sh <tool>`.
2. Use the returned version exactly.
3. If the script fails, stop and report the error.
4. Apply this rule to `mise.toml`, `rust-toolchain.toml`, Dockerfiles, CI files, and install docs.

Never invent versions for: rust, cargo, node, python, go, bun, uv, pnpm, terraform, kubectl.
